title: San Antonio Spurs vs Los Angles Lakers | November 3,2019
description: The Lakers defeated the Spurs, 103-96. LeBron James led the Lakers with 21 points, 11 rebounds and 13 assists, his second consecutive triple-double and the 83rd of his career. Additionally for the Lakers, Anthony Davis added 25 points and 11 rebounds, while Dejounte Murray recorded 18 points, 11 rebounds and 4 assists for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 5-1 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 4-2.
